@startuml
scale max 2480 width
scale max 3508 height
!theme plain
left to right direction
skinparam PackageStyle rectangle

actor "Standard User" as User
actor "Admin" as Admin

rectangle "Consent & AI Drafting System" {
    
    (Create Account) as UC1
    note right of UC1
      **As a** New User
      **I want to** register an account
      **So that** I can access t  he AI drafting platform.
      
      **Acceptance Criteria:**
      * System validates **Email** format and ensures it is unique.
      * Password meets complexity requirements and is salted/hashed.
      * User **MUST** accept the current **Active Term** version to proceed.
      * System records the specific **TermsId** and **Timestamp** of acceptance.
      * A default **Profile** entity is initialized for the user.
      * System generates a unique **OwnerId** to be used for all future file uploads.
    end note

    (Upload CV/Documents) as UC2
    note right of UC2
      **As a** User
      **I want to** upload my career documents to my profile
      **So that** they are stored centrally for multiple AI drafting jobs.
      
      **Acceptance Criteria:**
      * System validates file type (e.g., PDF, DOCX) and size limits.
      * File is uploaded to S3 and assigned a unique **S3Key**.
      * System records the **ChecksumHash** to prevent duplicate data processing.
      * File is tagged with **FileCategory** (Cv or RelevantDocuments).
      * The **S3File** reference is added to the user's **Profile** collection.
      * The user's **OwnerId** is stamped on the record for security.
    end note

    (Generate Application Draft) as UC3
    note right of UC3
      **As a** User
      **I want to** provide a job description and trigger the AI
      **So that** I receive a tailored CV or Cover Letter draft.
      
      **Acceptance Criteria:**
      * System retrieves **CurrentCv** and any selected **RelevantDocuments**.
      * System accepts Job Context (via URL scraping or PDF upload).
      * An **AIProcessingJob** record is created to track the request.
      * The **IAIService** runs inference and generates the text.
      * The result is saved as an **AiDraft** linked to the job.
    end note

    (Force Global Re-consent) as UC5
    note right of UC5
      **As an** Admin
      **I want to** update the terms for all users
      **So that** everyone is on the latest legal version.
      
      **Acceptance Criteria:**
      * Admin uploads new **Term** entity (S3 document + version string).
      * System sets the new Term as **Active** and deactivates the previous version.
      * System updates a **GlobalTermsVersion** timestamp/ID in the configuration.
      * On next request, the **ConsentService** identifies all users whose "LastAcceptedVersion" is less than current.
      * Affected users are blocked from AI services and redirected to the consent screen.
    end note

    (Anonymize Account/Retract account consent) as UC_Anonymize
    note right of UC_Anonymize
      **As a** User
      **I want to** anonymize my account
      **So that** my personal identity is removed but my contribution history remains.
      
      **Acceptance Criteria:**
      * System verifies User Identity.
      * **Email**, **Username**, and **Password** are overwritten with random GUIDs or "DELETED_USER".
      * **ProfileImage** and **Personal Details** are hard-deleted.
      * All linked **S3Files** are processed via the "File Scrub" logic (placeholder swap).
      * Account status is set to **Inactive/Anonymized**.
      * User is immediately logged out and cannot log back in with old credentials.
    end note


    (Delete Specific Document) as UC_DeleteDoc
    note right of UC_DeleteDoc
      **As a** User
      **I want to** delete a specific file (CV or Document)
      **So that** it is removed from the AIs context and S3 storage.
      
      **Acceptance Criteria:**
      * System verifies User owns the file via **OwnerId**.
      * File is deleted from physical S3 storage.
      * Record in **S3File** is modified to point to a file that says its removed.
      * AI Processing Jobs referencing this file are updated/flagged.
    end note

    (Login to System) as UC_Login
    note right of UC_Login
      **As a** Registered User (Standard or Admin)
      **I want to** authenticate with my credentials
      **So that** I can access my personalized dashboard and tools.
      
      **Acceptance Criteria:**
      * System validates **Email** and **Password** hash.
      * System checks **if user has consented to the latest terms** flag in the DB.
      * If terms are outdated, user is redirected to the Consent Screen.
      * JWT token includes the **UserRole** (User/Admin).
    end note

    (Download Document) as UC_Download
    note right of UC_Download
      **As a** User
      **I want to** download my CV, relevant documents, or AI drafts
      **So that** I can review them locally or submit them to employers.
      
      **Acceptance Criteria:**
      * System verifies User owns the file via **OwnerId**.
      * System generates a short-lived **S3 Presigned URL**.
      * Ensures file is still in a "Consented" state before providing the link.
    end note


    (Edit AI Draft) as UC_EditDraft
    note right of UC_EditDraft
      **As a** User
      **I want to** modify the draft generated by the AI
      **So that** I can personalize the content and correct any errors.
      
      **Acceptance Criteria:**
      * Original **AiDraft** entity remains read-only for audit/lineage.
      * System saves edited version as a new **S3File** with category **UserDraft**.
      * System links the new UserDraft to the original **AIProcessingJob**.
      * User can only save 1 edited version of the ai draft.
    end note

    (Upload Application-Specific File) as UC_AppFile
    note right of UC_AppFile
    **As a** User
    **I want to** upload a document for one specific job application
    **So that** it is only used as context for that specific AI draft.
    
    **Acceptance Criteria:**
    * File is tagged with **FileCategory.RelevantDocuments**.
    * System creates a link between the **S3File** and the **AIProcessingJob**.
    * File is NOT added to the user''s permanent **Profile** collection.
    * System automatically sets an expiry/cleanup flag if the application is deleted.
      end note

}

User --> UC_AppFile
User --> UC_EditDraft
User --> UC_Download
User --> UC_Login
Admin --> UC_Login
User --> UC_DeleteDoc
User --> UC1
User --> UC2
User --> UC3
User --> UC_Anonymize

Admin --> UC5
@enduml